3%2F214205_706a9f95db992bf0a54b5e75bdbae86e.jpg&h=7acc9bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我多數都係自己預時間去攞返堆衫。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T13:55:57.000Z","msg":"就係APA個D啦<br />\n<br />\n不過我次次都無㨂APA  <br />\n<br />\n住過ターミナルホテル group 既"},{"pid":"fca7cdbabc1b2fe98484318bd9e230e4d167b4f1","tid":727980,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:36:06.000Z","msg":"當然要預時間返去啦"},{"pid":"52d3a1b21d96d5ac688b798593b8c0d1c3ada2d8","tid":727980,"uid":180459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T14:44:06.000Z","msg":"我通常都係搵一晚早d（9點）返酒店，放落洗衣機後就返房打機睇電視，差唔多時間就返去拎，乾衣嘅時候一樣返房。乾衣無可能十分鐘搞掂，洗連乾預兩個鐘。"},{"pid":"93371c024c7f7c8bc2aaf8077d0b2fe3c58e7cb4","tid":727980,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"試過有間酒店部洗衣乾衣機要set密碼先開始<br />\n洗完就要入密碼先開到個蓋<br />\n唔怕俾其他住客搞到你啲衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e297afdc5295c189d0d87932e9c50f4517b4b2c1","tid":727980,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93371c024c7f7c8bc2aaf8077d0b2fe3c58e7cb4","tid":727980,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"試過有間酒店部洗衣乾衣機要set密碼先開始<br />\n洗完就要入密碼先開到個蓋<br />\n唔怕俾其他住客搞到你啲衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:46:05.000Z","msg":"正<br />\n<br />\n一過唔記得密碼就...."},{"pid":"9f40430c61a0bcfb9f50a6e1844ba2462844dccc","tid":727980,"uid":74171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e297afdc5295c189d0d87932e9c50f4517b4b2c1","tid":727980,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"93371c024c7f7c8bc2aaf8077d0b2fe3c58e7cb4","tid":727980,"uid":11890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:31:58.000Z","msg":"試過有間酒店部洗衣乾衣機要set密碼先開始<br />\n洗完就要入密碼先開到個蓋<br />\n唔怕俾其他住客搞到你啲衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T15:46: